title: Policy6190(III)
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Class rank will not be reported on student transcripts. School counselors will furnish a student's class rank via a separate letter to post-secondary institutions that require class rank for admissions and scholarship decisions. School counselors will inform students of their class rank upon request.

The Superintendent or designee shall be responsible for implementing this policy and developing procedures in furtherance of this policy, if necessary.
